To enable the network auto config on boot:

1. Copy waco-net-conf.sh to /usr/local/bin/
2. Copy waco-net-conf.service to /etc/systemd/system/
3. Set permissions chmod 744 /usr/local/bin/waco-net-conf.sh
4. Set permissions chmod 644 /etc/systemd/system/waco-net-conf.service
5. Run systemctl daemon-reload
6. Run systemctl enable waco-net-conf.service --now

